title: 3D Roller face Massager
description: A rejuvenating beauty roller that deeply kneads the skin and muscles on par with a luxurious, professional facial massage. Relieves facial tension Improves skin elasticity by tightening and toning the skin Reduces the appearance of fine lines Reduces dark circles around the eyes Promotes penetration of beauty products such as face creams Promotes blood circulation to the face for a healthy, natural glow Always start with clean skin that has been prepped with skincare product. Begin with the neck and roll the Tension Melting Massager along the base of the neck and the shoulders. Due to the special shape and angle of the double rollers, you will feel a deep kneading massage. Moving to the face, roll the massager in an outwards and upwards direction across the contours of the face. Breathe deeply and feel the tension melt away. Due to natural variations in stones, every roller is unique in pattern and color. Warn before use Remove accessories such as necklaces, earrings. Stack the hair or firm it with the hair band, to avoid tangling, and the massage will be more gentle. Use the bobby pin for short hair. For dry or sensitive skin, please apply a little lotion before use or Vitamin C Serum

title: CELESTIAL CAT CRYSTAL SHELF
description: ✦ Introducing our new Celestial Cat Shelf shelf ✦ An original wooden design handcrafted by Kate and her small team at Coppermoon to bring a bit of magic and sacredness to your home. She has embedded stars in her body and a gold tinted mirror in her tail. She is made out of poplar wood and stained in a choice of dark brown and oak colour for the ginger cat and a matt black colour with Gold for the Black cat. You can choose to either have one cat facing to the left or the right or both cats to create a magical cat scene in your home! This piece is primarily designed to sit on a flat surface but it can also be hung using the included attachments Dimensions 41 cm High x 31 cm Wide x 3.6 cm Deep (for storage)

title: Ear Cleaner Wax Removal
description: Ear Wax Removal device  wirelessly streams a full view of the inside of your ear to your iPhone or Android device, connects seamlessly over WiFi.it uses high brightness LED lights to illuminate the ear canal and achieve a clear image with an integrated waterproof camera to see and target wax easily and painless. Our wax removal kit can help you  illuminate the ear inspection area and capture more realistic images, which is easier to help you to check whether there is ear infection inside or remove the earwax safely, and suitable for daily ear cleaning care and professional examination of ear diseases.  Built-in WiFi hotspot and 3mm diameter camera lens, can realize clear image of earwax removal and full real-time video, rich in detail, convenient for real observation and auditory canal inspection . High brightness LED lights can provide auxiliary lighting to help improve image clarity in dark or low light conditions. It is widely compatible with Android and iOS smartphones and tablets, which makes connection more convenient. The waterproof camera lens can enter the body more easily and painlessly, and is suitable for eyes, nose, mouth, skin and other parts. Please scan QR code to download Android or IOS app. After app installed, please long press power button to turn on the ear pen. Then we will see led lights are lighting and hotspot wifi is ready to be connected. Click"Connection" to find hotspot wifi in mobile phone wifi settings and connect it successfully. Then we can click"Start" to enter into the display screen.

title: EMS Face Massager
description: All estheticians know that boosting healthy blood and lymphatic circulation are both essential in every effective facial. By using warming and cooling sensations on our skin for just 2 minutes a day, we get the benefits of healthy circulation. Our Hot & Cold Galvanic LED Facial Massager with EMS gives you maximum collagen boosting benefits with 2 forms of LED plus lifting EMS therapy. The Dirt in Deep Pores Is Discharged Through Biological Current and Thoroughly Cleaned Using the Principle of Positive and Negative Ion Inter-Attraction. Iontophoresis allows cosmetic ingredients to penetrate the skin’s bottom layer. Mechanical Vibration and Voltage Stimulation Have Been Used to Tighten Human Skin, Increase Elasticity, and Improve Skin Cell Metabolism. Warm massage promotes absorption, stretches the skin’s texture, and plumps the skin. Blue and Red Light Function: Improves skin elasticity, sagging, and wrinkles. Blue light therapy (wavelength 470nm – 10nm) is a type of light therapy that uses blue light. Blue light is particularly effective in the treatment of acne. Your skin will be disinfected because of this. Blue light also aids in the healing of inflammation. Skin Tightening, Brighten Skin Color, Resist Wrinkles, Remove Wrinkles, Remove Face, and Clean Detoxification are the four modes available. Apply a serum and moisturizer on dry, clean skin. Turn on the device to your preferred treatment mode, level of intensity, and red or blue LED. massage the skin in circular motions.

title: IPL Hair Removal 300000 flash
description: IPL Hair Removal  can be used on any body part in just a few minutes, all from the comfort of your own home! The  IPL Hair Removal  has 10+ years of flashes when used as recommended so you will be able to be hair free for a very long time! Quick and easy: each session only takes a few minutes once per week. Most advanced : Equipped with Intense Pulsed Light technology. Safe to use: use almost anywhere including arms, armpits, legs, chest, bikini, stomach, back, and FCS  More efficient : Our auto-slide flash technology rapidly speeds up session time. Quick results : Visible results in just a few sessions. Use at home : Use on your own time in the convenience of your own home. Remove excess hair by shaving, epilating, or waxing the area before the first treatment Select the correct intensity level Turn the unit on and press the Mini system to your skin. Wait for the flash light to turn on and press the flash button To achieve best results, use it every two weeks for the first two months and then do a monthly touch-up.For the first use, it is recommended to use level 1, and slowly strengthen according to the effect.

title: LUNA MOTH LAMP CRYSTAL SHELF
description: ✦ Luna Moth wooden crystal shelf ✦ An original wooden design handcrafted by Kate and her small team at Coppermoon to bring a bit more magic and sacredness into your home.  This beautiful Luna moth lamp design will be a unique place to display your crystals and keepsakes. The shelf is powered by 3 x AA batteries and can easily be turned on and off without taking the lamp off the wall. Made out of Poplar wood and stained in a dark Brown colour with solid Pine wooden shelves Luna moths are magical creatures! They are born, they transform, they love, they die, and then are again reborn. Their cycles are short, as are our years while we are here. We are reminded to make the most of our moments and to live and love to the fullest. She is most often seen in the evenings, attracted to the moon and to light. She speaks of our connection to the Feminine, our inner spirit, and our trust in ourselves. We learn of the importance to find the balance between light and dark, the seen and the unseen. She is a reminder that when all is said and done, our healing and sense of love are the ultimate journey. Dimensions cm Height: 27cm, Width:  43 cm Depth for crystal storage: 4.4cm

description: Due to the difficulty of production, only the last 180 pieces are left in the inventory, And the original price is $239.99, but now it's only $59.95. They will be removed when sold out. Special Design Perfect Garden Decoration Each blade of this yard spinner is designed to spin in different directions, ball bearing construction allows our wind catcher to quietly spin even in the slightest breeze. Maximum recommended wind 70 mph.🧡【LIGHT UP YOUR GARDEN WITH SEASONAL COLOR AND IMPRESS YOUR NEIGHBORS】-- easily seen and admired by passers-by but not intrusive to neighbors. Relaxing to watch while spending time out on the sun porch or yard. Would look amazing in any.❤️【STABLE, STURDY WITH MODERN FUNCTIONALITY & ANTIQUE CHARM】-- Many wind spinners outdoor come with a single blade that spins in one direction. Our solar wind spinner has a solid metallic construction with dual wind motion. The two tiers blades smoothly rotate in opposite directions on sealed bearings. Featuring modern functionality with period charm, our durable yard wind spinners have a stability stake at the base to ensure its firmly planted for windy days. ❤️【EASY TO INSTALL】-- This gardening decoration is easy to assemble with the instructions and no additional wiring, just simply position it in a sunny location with the metal stake and enjoy your garden ornament. ❤️【WEATHER RESISTANT】-- Our kinetic metal wind spinners come with multi-color brushed coat finishes and a stable stake at the base, which is built to withstand all weather, sturdy and durable for windy days. ❤️【HIGH QUALITY】-- This garden spinner is constructed with durable iron metal components and a long-lasting combo finish of paint and foil, bright metallic and reflective painting creates a visual sensation in the garden. ❤️【MADE IN USA】-- We are a very small family-owned manufacturing company which started out in our home garage. We now own a large warehouse where we manufacture and hand package our products. Support American Business FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS  Live in the southwest, will the paint colors stand up to excessive summer heat 100+ degrees without bubbling or pealing off? I live in the NW and have had 2 summers with it and colors are still great. 1st year summer was 100 and second summer was 98. Can The height of the spinner be adjusted to lower? You could remove the middle section of the metal post to make it shorter. The sections of pipe could be inter changible. All parts solid metal? All parts is metal. It is very sturdy. Will the wind spinner rotate in both directions? It spins in every direction the wind blows. The wheels rotate independently and it turns both directions to take advantage of every wind there is. How do you secure it so it doesn’t fall over the wind? The bottom post has 3 spiked feet that you stand on to drive them into the ground. Very firm and stable!.

description: SOMETHING BACKLESS, WE ARE THE SOLUTION. Say hello to our backless body bra. We broke the internet with it. And now we want you to look and feel your BEST at all times. 👗 It is usually worn under wedding dresses, party dresses, and a variety of low-cut clothes and necklines. HOW CAN I STYLE IT? Several styling options: The straps can be adjusted to be worn with halter style dresses, low-cut front, and criss-cross styles New removable invisible straps: Improved and durable. Completely seamless and imperceptible Designed to move with your body: Silky feeling! Sit, dance, and stretch with ease New Push-Up jumper: Well designed for support and raised bust - a serious push boost  Sticky glue: To keep the garment attached to the body without it slipping off Seamless string back with hook & loop closure: Smooths camel toe and gives you easy access to the bathroom 84% Nylon, 16% Spandex This body has been designed to facilitate the wearing of your dresses or halter tops. With adjustable straps and transparent anti-slip bars, our product disappears under your clothes.  PUSH-UP BH With its light pillows, our body will lift your breasts and give them a more rounded look. title: Queen Bee Crystal Drop Earrings
description: Bee populations are declining rapidly due to climate change, pesticides, pollution, habitat loss and decreasing in crop diversity.  Together we can protect them and keep our friendly bees buzzing and raise awareness of how important they are to us.   Wear these earrings with pride, knowing that a % of your purchase will go towards different organizations to help and save bees to keep the Buzzinggg! This will ensure that our bees are kept safe and reduce the declining of their population and raise awareness of their importance. Not only these bee earrings are adorable, they are also very fashionable as well. The earring will definitely turn heads and be noticed, and it can acts as a reminder that you have helped the bee colonies which plays a huge importance to us all. Our earrings are nickel, lead and cadmium free and it is also hypoallergenic so it is perfect for everyday wear.
